<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TV37">
<l>koṭuṅkāṟ cilaiyar niraikō ḷuḻavar kolaiyilveyya</l>
<l>kaṭuṅkā liḷaiñar tuṭipaṭuṅ kavvait taruviṉaiyē</l>
<l>ṉeṭuṅkāla muṅkaṇṇa ṉīṇmalarp pātam paravippeṟṟa</l>
<l>toṭuṅkā lociyu miṭaiyiḷa māṉceṉṟa cūḻkaṭamē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>It is noisy, sounding with the drums of swift-footed young warriors</l>
<l>hot in murder, of bent-legged bowmen [and] herd-seizing ploughmen,</l>
<l>– the wilderness around, where the young doe with a waist that breaks when touched has gone,</l>
<l>begotten by me with difficult Karma by revering Kaṇṇaṉ’s long blossom feet for a long time.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
